snippet.title: HorrorBuzz
snippet.description:
Horror, Haunted Houses, VR , Maze Walkthroughs, Halloween, Haunt News, 

HorrorBuzz is a channel that is the one stop for scary movies, theme park haunts and halloween events, independent haunts, horror games, and spooky, family friendly fun. We believe that scares shouldn’t be contained to Halloween, but should live all year long.

HorrorBuzz aims to accommodate the entire spectrum of scary tastes throughout the year by offering information on anything a horror fan might want to know; news, reviews, interviews, random videos that are scary, and breaking horror updates.
